title: Bones Beneath My Feet
description: Friendship, love, duty, loyalty, ambition. These were the tales of the heart. Neema and Titus were born in one fateful night shrouded in sword and victory. Neema grew to an elite warrior and Titus the crown prince of the prosperous Namian Empire. Something sinister is coming, and these two will do whatever is necessary for the empire.
author: Eden Snow
